title: Hour 1 - Browns and Baker, Tim MacMahon
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Browns and Baker, Tim MacMahon
description:
Dan considers the possibility of the Browns and Baker Mayfield reconciling if Deshaun Watson is suspended the entire year as looks likely. And he talks to Tim McMahon about the latest happenings in the NBA.
